<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>547 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/547/</link><description>Recent content in 547 on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/547/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] SQL Server Error 547: CHECK Constraint Failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlserver/error-547/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlserver/error-547/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="error-547-check-constraint-failed"&gt;Error 547: CHECK Constraint Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Error 547 occurs when an INSERT or UPDATE violates a CHECK constraint defined on the table. The data value does not satisfy the constraint&amp;rsquo;s validation rule.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The inserted value falls outside the allowed range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The value does not match the required pattern or format&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A NULL value is inserted into a column with a CHECK constraint that excludes NULLs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The constraint was added after existing data was already inconsistent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="identify-the-constraint"&gt;Identify the Constraint&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Find CHECK constraints on the table
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; name, definition
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; sys.check_constraints
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; parent_object_id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; OBJECT_ID(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;your_table&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="view-constraint-definition"&gt;View Constraint Definition&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXEC&lt;/span&gt; sp_helpconstraint &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;your_table&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-data-before-insert"&gt;Check Data Before Insert&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- See what values currently exist
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DISTINCT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;column_name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; your_table;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Verify the new value matches the constraint rules
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="modify-the-constraint"&gt;Modify the Constraint&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Drop existing constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; your_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_column_range;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Add updated constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; your_table
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_column_range &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CHECK&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;column_name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AND&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;column_name&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="temporarily-disable-constraint-use-cautiously"&gt;Temporarily Disable Constraint (Use Cautiously)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; your_table NOCHECK &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_column_range;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Fix the data
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Re-enable
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; your_table &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CHECK&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_column_range;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Age range constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_age &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CHECK&lt;/span&gt; (age &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;AND&lt;/span&gt; age &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;150&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (name, age) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;200&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error 547: The INSERT statement conflicted with the CHECK constraint &amp;#34;CK_age&amp;#34;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Status constraint
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; orders &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CONSTRAINT&lt;/span&gt; CK_status &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CHECK&lt;/span&gt; (status &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IN&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;pending&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;shipped&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;delivered&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;));
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; orders (status) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;unknown&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error 547: CHECK constraint violated
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlserver/error-8152/"&gt;Error 8152&lt;/a&gt; — string data truncation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlserver/error-1205/"&gt;Error 1205&lt;/a&gt; — deadlock victim&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>